  "keyFeatures": [
    "Super-fast runtime validators (20,000x faster than class-validator) via TypeScript transformation",
    "Type-safe JSON serialization 200x faster than class-transformer",
    "LLM function calling harness that improves accuracy from 6.75% to 100%",
    "Protocol Buffer encoding/decoding from pure TypeScript types",
    "Random data generation conforming to TypeScript type constraints",
    "Validation type tags (minimum, maximum, pattern, format, etc.) as TypeScript branded types",
    "Zero-schema approach — only pure TypeScript types required",
    "Support for unplugin ecosystem (Vite, Webpack, Rollup, esbuild, Next.js, Bun)"
  ],
